CD Baby Sales Data Crawler Software: Written by: Jonathan J.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CDBabySalesDataCrawler
    This is the web crawler implementation class for crawling the CDBaby site and downloading sales information.
    CDBabySalesDataCrawlerUI
    This is the UI and main program for the Willful Wreckords, LLC CDBaby Sales Data Crawler Application for scraping the CDBaby website and downloading artists sales data.
